examples.en: Somebody's car alarm kept me awake all night.
Somebody's been monkeying with my papers again.
He didn't want somebody's death on his conscience.
Somebody's been buggering about with my record player.
How old's your little girl (=somebody's young daughter) now?
Somebody's fingerprints are all along the bottom edge of the photograph.
I suppose somebody's got to make an army. *
Mind out! Somebody's trying to open the door. *
Somebody's been buggering about with my stereo. *
When the meat wagon stops at all the traffic lights on the way to the hospital you know somebody's pifted. *
